comment: Crawford (LAC) does not restrict Leonard's (SAS) FOM on the off-ball cut.
Barnes (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position while Paul (LAC) makes incidental foot to foot contact as they defend Diaw's (SAS) driving layup attempt.
Diaw (SAS) and Barnes (LAC) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Prior to Green (SAS) cleanly blocking the layup attempt, Duncan (SAS) makes incidental contact with Griffin's (LAC) arm.
Parker (SAS) initiates the contact with Redick (LAC) who turns only after contact while contesting the driving layup attempt.
RHH shows that Barnes (LAC) makes incidental contact with Parker's (SAS) body on the put back shot attempt prior to him landing.
Parker (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Crawford's (LAC) driving layup attempt.
Griffin (LAC) sets the screen on Green (SAS) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Duncan (SAS) makes "high-five" contact with Griffin (LAC) after the release of the jump shot, which is legal.
Crawford (LAC) and Green (SAS) make incidental contact with one another on the perimeter.
Duncan (SAS) does not give Paul (LAC) room to land on the jump shot.
Duncan (SAS) sets the screen on Redick (LAC) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Prior to the cleanly blocked shot by Barnes (LAC), Redick's (LAC) left arm makes contact with Duncan (SAS) that affects his movement to the basket and layup attempt.
Green (SAS) does not affect Paul's (LAC) RSBQ at the start of the drive.
Paul (LAC) makes incidental contact with Green (SAS), who maintains legal guarding position as he defends the driving layup attempt.
Ginobili (SAS) and Griffin (LAC) make incidental contact during rebounding.
The clock starts prior to the inbounds by San Antonio and is immediately reset.
Griffin (LAC) does not affect Leonard's (SAS) FOM as he defends during the inbounds play.

Griffin (LAC) and Barnes (LAC) maintain legal guarding positions as they defend the inbounds alley-oop pass intended for Leonard (SAS). Leonard makes incidental contact with Griffin as he jumps to receive the pass.
